HEADWORD: Gravery
<hw>Grav"er*y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act, process, or
art, of graving or carving; engraving.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Either of picture or <qex>gravery</qex> and embossing.</q>
